const overview = `The Mohare Danda Trek is a spectacular, sustainable journey through the heart of the Annapurna region. This community-based trail offers an authentic alternative to the crowded Poon Hill route, taking you through lush rhododendron forests and vibrant Magar villages. Balancing cultural immersion in Kathmandu with high-altitude serenity, the trek culminates at the Mohare ridge. It provides hikers with intimate homestay experiences and unobstructed, front-row views of the Dhaulagiri and Annapurna massifs, making it perfect for eco-conscious adventurers seeking tranquility.`;
